1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,000
Stop optimizing your morning.
Fix your evening first.

2
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:08,000
Everyone obsesses over morning routines. Cold showers. Journaling. Meditation. But
if your evening is chaos, your morning won't matter.

3
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:18,000
Your morning energy is decided the night before. Screen time,
caffeine timing, and wind-down routine set up tomorrow's focus.

4
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:24,000
One rule: dim your lights and stop
screens 60 minutes before bed. That's it.

5
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:30,000
Link in bio — free
energy profile in 30 seconds.

